(T2 D=0.375 CR=0. - ZMIN=-0.3937 - flat end mill)

M0 (Read note)
(With parameter #35 set to 0 each tool will cycle through the spindle)
(to verify that the correct tool is in the tool magazine and to automatically measure it.)
(Once the tools are verified set parameter #35 to 1 with)
(an MDI command of '#35 = 1' to skip verification.)
(The value of parameter #35 can be checked with a '(DEBUG, #35)' command.)
(The value will be shown on the Status page.)
o100 sub
o110 if [#35 LT 1]
(T1  D=2. CR=0. - face mill)
T1 M6 (MEASURE TOOL)
G37
(T2  D=0.375 CR=0. - flat end mill)
T2 M6 (MEASURE TOOL)
G37
o110 endif
o100 endsub

